snippet.title: Magicka: Wizard Wars Open Beta Trailer
snippet.description: As of today, anybody can download and play Magicka: Wizard Wars and try their hand at the elementary arcane arts in the spellcasting action player-vs-player (PvP) game where misspelling is deadly. Get access now: http://access.wizardwars.com/
